Class ImmutableList<T>

java.lang.Object
  org.odata4j.core.ImmutableList<T>
Type Parameters:
T - the list item type
All Implemented Interfaces:
Iterable<T>, Collection<T>, List<T>, RandomAccess
public class ImmutableList<T>
extends Object
implements List<T>, RandomAccess

A List implementation whose structure is immutable after construction.

Useful for apis that assume a returned list remains unmodified.

All mutation methods throw UnsupportedOperationException
